                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3895" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0117</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8488 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">围绕明星的资本运作——“星星”之火，可以燎原</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Capital Operation Around Stars——The spark can start a prairie fire</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">甘丽凝，黄瀚乐</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐德影视</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资本运作；明星绑定；风险与收益</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Capital operation; Star binding; Risks and benefits</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了与女星范冰冰深度绑定的影视公司——浙江唐德影视股份有限公司。2014年年底，公司出品的《武媚娘传奇》开播后一路飘红，2015年其在深交所上市，2016年深度绑定王牌明星——范冰冰。这样一个前途光明的公司却在2018年因为微博上的几句话和几张图片陷入困境。一个明星引发的火种，可以让一个公司红红火火，扶摇直上，也能成为燎原之火，让公司发展之路运途多舛。明星到底有怎样的能量？唐德影视到底是怎样被影响的？本案例描述了唐德影视与范冰冰合作的过程以及阴阳合同事件发生后唐德影视的状况。着重分析了二者合作中运用的资本运作手段，以及明星对影视公司业绩与价值的影响。本案例旨在引导学生分析公司之间的资本运作模式，讨论明星绑定商业模式的风险与收益，提高学生分析能力和决策能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes a film company, Zhejiang TangDe Film Co., Ltd., which is deeply bound to actress Fan Bingbing. At the end of 2014, the company&#39;s &quot;The Empress of China&quot; became popular all the way after its launch. It was listed on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange in 2015 and deeply bound the leading light star Fan Bingbing in 2016. Such a promising company was in trouble in 2018 because of a few words and pictures on Weibo. A star can make a company prosperous and rocking up, can also become a prairie fire, and make the company&#39;s development path worse. What kind of energy do stars have? How on earth was TangDe Co., Ltd. influenced? This case describes the process of cooperation between TangDe Co., Ltd. and Fan Bingbing, and the situation of TangDe Co., Ltd. after the twin-contracts. The case focuses on the capital operation means used in the cooperation between them, and the influence of stars on the performance and value of film and television companies. The purpose of this case is to guide students to analyze the capital operation mode between companies, discuss the risks and benefits of star-binding business model, and improve students&#39; analytical and decision-making abilities.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司战略与风险管理》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资本运作  绕明星资本运作商业模式 风险理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
